#30daysofdance 
Day 17
Challenge: Rhythm Layering

@kevin_paradox 

This challenge made me sweat tears.So much intense this challenge is.
Did front back step and the box step with some body grooves,isolations and angels.

#30daysofdance#freestyle#hiphopbeats

#30daysofchallenge
Day 9
Challenge : Elements of Nature
First community challenge 

@kevin_paradox 

Used few elements like wind,water ,earth and (little bit ) fire but more than that I focused on the part where I could express as an element itself.

#hiphop#dance#freestyle#music#elementsofnature

#30daysofdance
Day 4 
Challenge - Swinging legs
@kevin_paradox 

Tried adding some foundation steps,top rock and house . Had so much in head to apply but when got down implementing I barely could cover much and just passed with the flow.The challenge is harder than it seems.
My legs hurt ;) Will try getting better at this.

#30daysofdance
Day 2
Challenge : 1 movement throughout

Okay it was challenging but so engaging .I could connect with every movement and most importantly I have never been this patient. I will try being more aware with my movements, this challenge was a great learning

Grateful | Thankful to @kevin_paradox 🙏😇

latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy Independence Day 🇮🇳
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@iimp_bba Indira celebrates Independence Day asking questions to the students.😍

We emerged with a wholly varied notion, where we the students expressed what arrives in our psyche when we think of the term freedom.😇😇

Being Independent offers us the freedom and flexibility to live life the way we choose, whether from a financial, political, relationship, or career standpoint. Not relying on anyone else to do everything for us unlocks countless possibilities. 
Celebrating 74 years of Independence. 🇮🇳

#iimp#indiracollege#independenceday#freedom#students#sovereignity#liberty#celebratinglife
